<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Scope on LLHISME'S Blog</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/tags/scope/</link><description>Recent content in Scope on LLHISME'S Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>vi</language><managingEditor>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</managingEditor><webMaster>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://llhisme.github.io/tags/scope/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>JavaScript Cơ Bản #3: Hàm (Functions) và Scope</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/post/javascript/javascript-co-ban-3/</link><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</author><guid>https://llhisme.github.io/post/javascript/javascript-co-ban-3/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="hàm-là-gì"&gt;Hàm là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hàm&lt;/strong&gt; (Function) là một khối code có thể tái sử dụng, thực hiện một nhiệm vụ cụ thể. Hàm giúp code trở nên có tổ chức, dễ đọc và dễ bảo trì.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="các-cách-định-nghĩa-hàm"&gt;Các cách định nghĩa hàm&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-function-declaration-khai-báo-hàm"&gt;1. Function Declaration (Khai báo hàm)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="kd"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;tinhTong&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="2-function-expression-biểu-thức-hàm"&gt;2. Function Expression (Biểu thức hàm)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="kr"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;tinhHieu&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kd"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="3-arrow-function-hàm-mũi-tên---es6"&gt;3. Arrow Function (Hàm mũi tên - ES6)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="kr"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;tinhTich&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="scope-phạm-vi"&gt;Scope (Phạm vi)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Scope xác định khả năng truy cập của các biến.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>